<h4>Search Tips</h4>
<div class="combo-box-hr"><hr/></div>
<p class="issue-specific-tips">Easily find issues by searching: <b>#&lt;Issue ID&gt;</b><br/>Example: #1832</p>
<p class="member-specific-tips">Easily find members by searching in: <b>&lt;username&gt;</b>, <b>&lt;first name&gt;</b> and <b>&lt;last name&gt;</b>.<br/><br/>Example: Search <b>smith</b>, will return results <b>smith</b> and <b>adamsmith</b></p>
<div class="solr-search-tips">
You can use:<ul>
<li>Boolean operators AND, OR and NOT (must be in caps, e.g. oracle AND debugger, debugger NOT oracle)</li>
<li>Single and multiple character wildcard (e.g. de?ug, debug*)</li>
<li>Grouping (e.g. ((oracle debugger) AND exception))</li>
<li>Quoted phrase (e.g. "Oracle Debugger")</li>
</ul>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
$j(document).ready(function () {
initTreeEvents();
});

function showFilterDialog(filterUrl) {
app.doAjaxWithRetry("get", filterUrl, {}, function (json) {
$j(json.markup).appendTo(document.body);
var dialog = $j('#modal-search');
var setupHandler = window[$j(dialog).data('setup')];
setupHandler();
});
}

function showSearchOptions() {
var filterQuery = "";
var showFilterUrl = "/ajax/home/project/public/aquadatastudio/issue/filter/new?viewName=standard";
if (filterQuery) {
showFilterUrl += "&" + filterQuery;
}
showFilterDialog(showFilterUrl);
}

function createFilter() {
var showFilterUrl = "/ajax/home/project/public/aquadatastudio/issue/filter/new?viewName=standard&clearFilter=true";
showFilterDialog(showFilterUrl);
}

function editFilter(filterId) {
var actionUrl = "/ajax/home/project/public/aquadatastudio" + "/issue/filter/" + filterId + "/edit" + "?viewName=standard";
showFilterDialog(actionUrl);
}

function deleteFilter(filterId) {
var actionUrl = "/ajax/home/project/public/aquadatastudio" + "/issue/filter/" + filterId + "/delete";
var $node = $j("#" + filterId);
var nodeId = (filterId === 'all') ? '' : filterId;
app.confirmDelete({
title:'Delete Filter',
question:'Are you sure you want to delete this filter?',
description:app.escapeHTML($j(".tree-node-label", $node).text()),
primaryActionLabel:'Delete Filter',
submitUrl:actionUrl,
deleteId:nodeId,
actionCallback:function (json) {
if (json.status) {
if (!nodeId) {
app.saveMessage(json.message, "alert alert-success");
window.location.href = "/app/home/project/public/aquadatastudio/issue?viewName=standard";
} else {
app.showTopMessage(json.message, "alert alert-success");
}
} else {
$j('#confirm-msgbox-body').html(json.message);
}
}
});
}

function initTreeEvents() {
$j("div.tree-node:has(a.tree-node-label)").click(function (event) {
var target = $j(event.target);
if (target.hasClass("tree-node")) {
window.location = $j("a.tree-node-label", this).attr("href");
} else if (target.hasClass("tree-node-twisty")) {
window.location = $j("a.tree-node-label", this).attr("href");
}
});
}

function showTreeMenuOptions(id1) {
$j('#' + id1).removeClass("invisible").addClass("visible");
}

function hideTreeMenuOptions(id1) {
var menu = $j('#' + id1);
if (menu.hasClass("open")) {
$j("html").on('click.dropdown.data-api', function () {
menu.removeClass("visible").addClass("invisible");
});
} else {
menu.removeClass("visible").addClass("invisible");
}
}
</script>
